    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed manual transmission and a Variable M Differential Lock for precise torque distribution. The vehicle exhibits excellent mechanical health, with the double-VANOS system operating smoothly across the power band. Significant preventative maintenance has been performed, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing service, addressing the primary longitudinal stress points of this chassis. While showing light patina consistent with a well-loved performance machine, the suspension geometry remains true and the hydraulic steering rack provides exceptional feedback. A turn-key enthusiast vehicle ready for the B-roads.",
